These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-1::.
There 7 different types of food: apple, apricot, kiwi, pineapple, radish, raspberry, spinach
City: prague, berlin, boston, marseilles, rome, colone, san-francisco
 1. the person eating kiwi is on the far left##1
 2. the person eating pineapple is not the person traveling to colone##6
 3. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
 4. the person traveling to san-francisco is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to rome##5
 5. the person eating radish is on the left or right of the person eating spinach##3
 6. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
 7. the person eating raspberry is somewhere between the person eating apricot and the person traveling to berlin##7
 8. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 9. the person traveling to marseilles is somewhere between the person eating radish and the person traveling to boston##7
10. the person traveling to boston is on the left or right of the person traveling to prague##3
11. the person traveling to rome is on the far left##1
12. the person eating pineapple is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##5
13. the person eating pineapple is somewhere to the right of the person eating raspberry##5
14. the person eating spinach is somewhere to the right of the person eating radish##5
15. the person eating radish is the person traveling to berlin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5     |     6     |    7    |
| Food          | kiwi    | apple    | apricot | raspberry | pineapple | radish    | spinach |
| City   | rome | prague | boston  | colone   | marseilles    | berlin | san-francisco |

