.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-2::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, cola, sprite, coffee, juice, milk, mirinda
The people have 7 different hobbies: camping, chess, gardening, hiking, rock-climbing, singing, skydiving
 1. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere between the person drinking mirinda and the person drinking cola##7
 2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person drinking coffee##1
 3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who's hobby is chess##7
 6. the person drinking milk is somewhere between the person drinking coffee and the person who's hobby is gardening##7
 7. the person drinking juice is somewhere between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking cola##7
 8. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 9. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the left of the person drinking juice##5
10. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is singing##5
11. the person who's hobby is singing is not the person drinking mirinda##6
12. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
13. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person drinking coffee##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |       5       |      6      |    7    |
| Beverage    | mirinda  | sprite | milk | coffee | iced-tea     | juice | cola  |
| Hobby   | gardening | singing | chess  | skydiving  | rock-climbing | hiking      | camping |

