.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-3::.
7 different games are played: billiard, chess, go, mah-jongg, backgammon, whist, monopoly
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: ambient, blues, country, d&b, hip-hop, jazz, metal
 1. the fan of metal is between the person playing go and the fan of country##2
 2. the person playing chess is somewhere to the right of the fan of blues##5
 3. the fan of blues is not the person playing mah-jongg##6
 4. the fan of ambient is somewhere to the right of the fan of jazz##5
 5. the fan of ambient is between the fan of jazz and the person playing backgammon##2
 6. the fan of country is somewhere to the right of the person playing mah-jongg##5
 7. the person playing monopoly is on the far right##1
 8. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
 9. the person playing go is somewhere between the fan of hip-hop and the fan of metal##7
10. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
11. the person playing backgammon is in an even position##4
12. the person playing backgammon is not the fan of ambient##6
13. the person playing whist is somewhere between the person playing chess and the person playing backgammon##7
14. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
15. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
16. the person playing backgammon is not the fan of jazz##6
17. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the fan of country##3
18. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
19. the fan of ambient is somewhere to the left of the fan of hip-hop##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |    4    |       5       |     6     |      7      |
| Game         | billiard | chess | whist | backgammon  | go | mah-jongg | monopoly |
| Music-Genre   | blues   | jazz       | ambient   | hip-hop | d&b           | metal     | country     |

