.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-4::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: golf, lacrosse, parkour, doging, skiing, tennis, volleyball
7 different pets are kept: chinchilla, pony, snake, dog, goldfish, frog, goat
 1. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the pony##5
 2. the person who's sport is parkour is in an odd position##4
 3. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goat##5
 4. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the right of the owner of the frog##5
 5. the person who's sport is doging is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##5
 6. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
 7. the owner of the snake is somewhere between the owner of the pony and the owner of the goldfish##7
 8. the person who's sport is doging is on the far left##1
 9. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is golf##5
10. the person who's sport is tennis is in an even position##4
11. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere between the person who's sport is skiing and the person who's sport is lacrosse##7
12. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##5
13. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
14. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goat##5
15. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
16. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the snake##5
17. the owner of the dog is between the person who's sport is tennis and the owner of the frog##2
18. the person who's sport is skiing is not the owner of the goat##6
19. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the right of the owner of the pony##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2    |     3     |     4      |     5      |    6    |    7     |
| Sport       | doging | golf    | parkour   | volleyball | skiing     | tennis  | lacrosse |
