 7. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to london##5
 8. the person who's sport is basketball is not the person traveling to venice##6
 9. the person traveling to london is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5
10. the person who's sport is snowboarding is not the person traveling to venice##6
11. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
12. the person traveling to london is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
13. the person traveling to new-york is not the person who's sport is biathlon##6
