.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-7::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: fuchsia, orange, ebony, chestnut, turquise, brown, white
The people use 7 different means of transport: airplane, bike, boat, helicopter, motorbike, snowmobile, van
 1. the person driving the motorbike is not the person who likes turquise##6
 2. the person who likes brown is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3
 3. the person driving the van is the person who likes chestnut##1
 4. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 5. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 6. the person driving the airplane is somewhere between the person who likes turquise and the person who likes white##7
 7. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 8. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
 9. the person who likes turquise is not the person driving the helicopter##6
10. the person who likes orange is in an even position##4
11. the person who likes orange is not the person driving the motorbike##6
12. the person driving the van is in the middle##1
13. the person driving the boat is between the person driving the motorbike and the person who likes ebony##2
14. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere between the person who likes chestnut and the person driving the boat##7
15. the person driving the bike is somewhere to the left of the person who likes brown##5
16. the person who likes white is on the left or right of the person driving the airplane##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2     |     3     |    4    |     5      |     6     |     7      |
