 3. the person eating strawberry is on the left or right of the person eating raspberry##3
 4. the person eating strawberry is the person eating strawberry##1
 5. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 6. the person playing go is somewhere between the person playing snooker and the person playing monopoly##7
 7. the person eating lemon is in an odd position##4
 8. the person playing monopoly is in an even position##4
 9. the person eating mango is the person playing backgammon##1
10. the person eating strawberry is between the person eating raspberry and the person playing go##2
11. the person eating blueberry is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
12. the person playing go is in the middle##1
13. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
14. the person eating pomegranate is on the left or right of the person eating strawberry##3
15. the person eating mango is on the far left##1
16. the person eating mango is somewhere to the left of the person playing poker##5
17. the person eating blueberry is somewhere to the right of the person playing monopoly##5
