 1. the person who growsmarigold is the fan of indie##1
 2. the person who growsaconite is somewhere to the left of the fan of ambient##5
 3. the person who growsiris is somewhere between the fan of soul and the fan of metal##7
 4. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
 5. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
 6. the fan of dubstep is not the person who growspoppy##6
 7. the person who growsrose is the fan of ambient##1
 8. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
 9. the person who growspoppy is somewhere to the left of the fan of ambient##5
10. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
11. the person who growspoppy is between the fan of gospel and the person who growsiris##2
12. the fan of rock is somewhere between the fan of soul and the person who growspoppy##7
13. the fan of indie is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
