.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-16::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: cricket, cycling, handball, skiing, snowboarding, swimming, tennis
There are 7 different favourite beverages: sprite, mirinda, water, milk, hot-chocolate, tea, cola
 1. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person drinking milk##7
 2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 3. the person drinking cola is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person who's sport is snowboarding##2
 4. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
 5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 6. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
 7. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5
 8. the person drinking tea is the person who's sport is skiing##1
 9. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
10. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
11. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5
12. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
13. the person drinking sprite is somewhere between the person who's sport is skiing and the person drinking milk##7
14. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person drinking mirinda##1
15. the person drinking cola is the person who's sport is cricket##1
16. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
17. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is tennis##5
18. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking tea##1

